Rex Lee (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rex_Lee_(actor) 0 Rex Lee (born January 7, 1969) is an American actor. He is best known for his recurring role as Lloyd Lee in the television series Entourage and his starring role as Elliot Park in the television sitcom Young Hungry.
